### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Login Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@igreja.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Dados do usuário logado
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Alterar senha
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "123456",
  "newPassword": "novaSenha123"
}

### Listar membros ativos
GET {{baseUrl}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar membros inativos
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/inactive
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar membro por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar membro
POST {{baseUrl}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João da Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "84999999999",
  "birthDate": "2000-05-20",
  "role": "MEMBRO"
}

### Atualizar membro
PUT {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João da Silva Atualizado",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "phone": "84999999999",
  "birthDate": "2000-05-20",
  "role": "VOLUNTARIO"
}

### Inativar membro
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Restaurar membro
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Listar movimentações
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar movimentações por tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?type=ENTRADA
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar movimentações por mês e ano
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?month=6&year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar movimentação por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar entrada de dízimo
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ENTRADA",
  "category": "DIZIMO",
  "value": 100,
  "description": "Dízimo mensal",
  "memberId": "{{memberId}}",
  "date": "2026-06-11"
}

### Criar saída/despesa
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "SAIDA",
  "category": "ENERGIA",
  "value": 250,
  "description": "Conta de energia",
  "date": "2026-06-11"
}

### Atualizar movimentação
PUT {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ENTRADA",
  "category": "OFERTA",
  "value": 150,
  "description": "Oferta corrigida",
  "date": "2026-06-11"
}

### Deletar movimentação
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Resumo geral do mês atual
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Resumo por mês e ano
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/summary?month=6&year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}